WEBVTT

00:00:29.323 --> 00:00:33.053
(On the second morning, the sons received a gift box each.)

00:00:33.168 --> 00:00:34.863
I'm told to ask a girl out on a date.

00:00:35.763 --> 00:00:39.833
(Winning present for a date from Dad)

00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:44.433
(The date requested with a gift is on a 1st-come, 1st-served basis.)

00:00:44.873 --> 00:00:47.803
(Yoon Hoo ran out first.)

00:00:48.073 --> 00:00:49.873
(Spare me a minute, Yu Bin.)

00:00:51.413 --> 00:00:53.343
Why am I here?

00:00:54.213 --> 00:00:59.083
(So nobody can snatch you away.)

00:00:59.283 --> 00:01:00.683
- "So nobody can snatch you away." - "So nobody can snatch you away."

00:01:00.853 --> 00:01:04.253
(The intense tough guy's bold move)

00:01:04.693 --> 00:01:06.753
(Go on a date with me.)

00:01:07.463 --> 00:01:10.293
(Yoon Hoo asked Choi Yu Bin on the 1st-come 1st-served Date.)

00:01:10.893 --> 00:01:12.593
(A date request)

00:01:13.703 --> 00:01:16.763
(Lee Jae Seung asked Park Si Woo on the 1st-come 1st-served Date.)

00:01:17.203 --> 00:01:19.103
(How about going on a date with me today?)

00:01:19.233 --> 00:01:21.203
(Shin Jae Hyuk asked Cho Eun Byul on the 1st-come 1st-served Date.)

00:01:21.343 --> 00:01:24.273
(Is Hee Dong all alone?)

00:01:24.513 --> 00:01:26.713
(I think you'll go on a date with the new resident.)

00:01:27.013 --> 00:01:29.883
(Apparently, he can ask the new resident out on a date.)

00:01:29.983 --> 00:01:31.452
(A new female resident will move in.)

00:01:31.453 --> 00:01:33.213
(Write a letter on the back of the photo.)

00:01:33.653 --> 00:01:35.652
(Hee Dong asked the new resident, whom he hadn't met yet, )

00:01:35.653 --> 00:01:37.623
(out on a date.)

00:01:39.353 --> 00:01:42.993
(How's the first date of our kids?)

00:01:44.463 --> 00:01:49.233
(Episode 3: Twisting Around One's Finger)

00:01:50.063 --> 00:01:51.972
(After the first date matching session)

00:01:51.973 --> 00:01:53.803
I didn't know you didn't add green onions.

00:01:54.703 --> 00:01:57.843
You're supposed to enjoy the bland taste of this dish.

00:01:58.543 --> 00:02:01.343
(Today's chef is Yu Bin.)

00:02:02.143 --> 00:02:04.312
Is it for someone or herself?

00:02:04.313 --> 00:02:05.313
Both.

00:02:05.314 --> 00:02:06.413
- Is that so?
- Yes.

00:02:07.883 --> 00:02:11.193
(After making food, she heads somewhere.)

00:02:13.693 --> 00:02:14.862
Is Yoon Hoo in here?

00:02:14.863 --> 00:02:15.863
She's asking for someone.

00:02:15.864 --> 00:02:16.963
- It's Yoon Hoo.
- Yoon Hoo.

00:02:18.033 --> 00:02:20.092
- What's up?
- You're going to eat, right?

00:02:20.093 --> 00:02:21.433
- Yes.
- Good.

00:02:21.463 --> 00:02:24.433
I'll be waiting.

00:02:24.533 --> 00:02:27.302
- Sorry, I'll be out in a second.
- Take your time.

00:02:27.303 --> 00:02:28.642
- Don't rush.
- I'll be out right away.

00:02:28.643 --> 00:02:29.942
Is she taking care of my son?

00:02:29.943 --> 00:02:31.372
She's taking care of him...

00:02:31.373 --> 00:02:32.412
And only him.

00:02:32.413 --> 00:02:33.443
- Jae Hyuk is there too.
- Already?

00:02:33.713 --> 00:02:35.382
To make fried rice of all things.

00:02:35.383 --> 00:02:36.882
- My son loves fried rice.
- For real.

00:02:36.883 --> 00:02:38.083
She likes fried rice.

00:02:40.383 --> 00:02:43.823
(Getting ready for the unexpected breakfast date)

00:02:51.063 --> 00:02:52.433
What's taking so long?

00:02:53.693 --> 00:02:56.263
(Even lip balm when he'll soon have fried rice?)

00:02:56.833 --> 00:02:59.333
- It's best eaten when warm.
- Exactly.

00:03:00.303 --> 00:03:03.243
(Rushing over)

00:03:04.143 --> 00:03:05.713
You weren't waiting for me, were you?

00:03:05.773 --> 00:03:07.142
- What?
- No, right?

00:03:07.143 --> 00:03:08.882
I was waiting for you. Why do you ask?

00:03:08.883 --> 00:03:10.243
- Really?
- Yes.

00:03:11.113 --> 00:03:13.152
- You should've told me.
- It's okay.

00:03:13.153 --> 00:03:14.253
(Yu Bin waited to eat with Yoon Hoo.)

00:03:14.453 --> 00:03:16.353
I put in some effort, you know?

00:03:17.453 --> 00:03:19.023
Thanks for the food.

00:03:19.153 --> 00:03:20.252
I hope you enjoy it.

00:03:20.253 --> 00:03:21.563
It looks good.

00:03:25.893 --> 00:03:27.062
It'll taste really bland.

00:03:27.063 --> 00:03:29.103
(Impressed)

00:03:30.163 --> 00:03:32.172
(Yoon Hoo's reaction makes Yu Bin laugh.)

00:03:32.173 --> 00:03:33.733
What a great reaction.

00:03:37.443 --> 00:03:38.773
It's really good.

00:03:39.643 --> 00:03:40.913
- Seriously?
- Yes.

00:03:42.083 --> 00:03:45.012
We're going to get food soon during our date.

00:03:45.013 --> 00:03:46.953
- I can eat more.
- No,

00:03:47.083 --> 00:03:49.523
but you can't enjoy the food on our date if you're full.

00:03:50.723 --> 00:03:52.422
- No way.
- Come on.

00:03:52.423 --> 00:03:53.923
"No way."

00:03:54.393 --> 00:03:56.462
- What was that?
- My gosh.

00:03:56.463 --> 00:03:57.863
He's acting cute.

00:03:59.363 --> 00:04:03.033
What I'm about to ask may sound weird.

00:04:07.003 --> 00:04:08.173
Will you make this...

00:04:09.403 --> 00:04:10.713
- What?
- even when we're married?

00:04:12.413 --> 00:04:13.943
Most likely.

00:04:15.513 --> 00:04:17.553
- Okay.
- Okay.

00:04:19.753 --> 00:04:21.282
- What?
- He's gone too far.

00:04:21.283 --> 00:04:22.582
Was that him proposing or what?

00:04:22.583 --> 00:04:23.852
- Mr. Yoon.
- What's up with him?

00:04:23.853 --> 00:04:25.122
Isn't he going too far?

00:04:25.123 --> 00:04:27.362
To talk about marriage when it's just fried rice.

00:04:27.363 --> 00:04:28.892
She said, "Most likely."

00:04:28.893 --> 00:04:31.193
Hold on. Is that the so-called American style?

00:04:31.833 --> 00:04:34.102
Even Americans aren't that big of a mess.

00:04:34.103 --> 00:04:36.132
- "Big of a mess?" - That's too fast.

00:04:36.133 --> 00:04:37.533
- It's too fast.
- Exactly.

00:04:37.773 --> 00:04:39.402
- It's only been a day.
- He's setting it in stone.

00:04:39.403 --> 00:04:41.142
It's only been a day, and he's talking about marriage.

00:04:41.143 --> 00:04:42.603
(Yoon Hoo's flirting created a big stir.)

00:04:44.143 --> 00:04:45.773
I suddenly imagined being married.

00:04:46.743 --> 00:04:49.413
"It'd be amazing to have this for breakfast every day."

00:04:50.413 --> 00:04:51.582
"What's going on?"

00:04:51.583 --> 00:04:54.653
With that, I was really shocked.

00:04:55.253 --> 00:04:56.923
But it still made me happy.

00:04:58.793 --> 00:04:59.952
It's seriously good.

00:04:59.953 --> 00:05:02.162
(Straight to marriage when they've only met yesterday?)

00:05:02.163 --> 00:05:04.763
The wedding march is being played right now.

00:05:04.863 --> 00:05:06.663
What's with the music?

00:05:10.003 --> 00:05:12.302
(Meanwhile, Jae Seung is in the living room all alone.)

00:05:12.303 --> 00:05:13.572
Jae Seung is alone.

00:05:13.573 --> 00:05:16.403
- That's how he always sits.
- Seriously.

00:05:17.343 --> 00:05:21.043
(Yoon Hoo came to relax after breakfast.)

00:05:21.543 --> 00:05:24.013
(Thinking)

00:05:24.983 --> 00:05:27.213
Did you get an Attraction Selection text yesterday?

00:05:27.553 --> 00:05:28.653
- Yes.
- I see.

00:05:30.823 --> 00:05:31.923
Did you?

00:05:32.223 --> 00:05:33.923
(Nodding)

00:05:34.893 --> 00:05:36.962
Do you have an idea who might've sent it?

00:05:36.963 --> 00:05:38.832
I have a hunch about who sent it to me,

00:05:38.833 --> 00:05:41.462
- Really?
- who you've sent one to,

00:05:41.463 --> 00:05:42.632
and who sent one to you.

00:05:42.633 --> 00:05:43.733
- For real?
- Yes.

00:05:45.473 --> 00:05:46.672
(Yoon Hoo knows everything?)

00:05:46.673 --> 00:05:47.903
- What?
- Really?

00:05:49.073 --> 00:05:52.843
(Last night during the first Attraction Selection)

00:05:53.413 --> 00:05:58.083
(Eun Byul was the one who sent it to Jae Seung.)

00:05:58.583 --> 00:05:59.983
From what I see,

00:06:01.653 --> 00:06:02.983
it's Si Woo.

00:06:03.523 --> 00:06:05.593
He's gotten the wrong idea.

00:06:05.893 --> 00:06:07.223
Don't do that.

00:06:07.893 --> 00:06:10.162
There's always that one friend who hypes things up.

00:06:10.163 --> 00:06:12.393
- Totally.
- I think she has a crush on you.

00:06:12.563 --> 00:06:13.632
- Really?
- Totally.

00:06:13.633 --> 00:06:14.662
Seriously?

00:06:14.663 --> 00:06:16.432
- I think you're wrong.
- It's Si Woo.

00:06:16.433 --> 00:06:18.102
- Si Woo is totally into you.
- Really?

00:06:18.103 --> 00:06:20.172
- Yes.
- Got it. I'll give it my best.

00:06:20.173 --> 00:06:21.442
The two are very alike.

00:06:21.443 --> 00:06:23.173
- Hoo is hasty.
- Right?

00:06:23.503 --> 00:06:24.913
Let's say he's pure-hearted.

00:06:25.943 --> 00:06:29.543
I asked her out in hopes that it's true.

00:06:31.613 --> 00:06:33.113
Here's what I'm worried about.

00:06:34.253 --> 00:06:37.653
I asked her out on the date, but she didn't look happy.

00:06:37.723 --> 00:06:41.663
Or I might just be imagining it.

00:06:42.723 --> 00:06:45.933
(When Jae Seung asked Si Woo out this morning)

00:06:46.163 --> 00:06:47.402
A date request.

00:06:47.403 --> 00:06:48.662
(Disappointed)

00:06:48.663 --> 00:06:49.833
Thank you.

00:06:51.703 --> 00:06:53.902
(Si Woo turned around quickly.)

00:06:53.903 --> 00:06:55.302
What?

00:06:55.303 --> 00:06:56.342
(Surprised)

00:06:56.343 --> 00:06:58.312
- She acted coldly.
- That's so wrong.

00:06:58.313 --> 00:07:00.042
- She did.
- I see.

00:07:00.043 --> 00:07:03.243
- Right.
- It hurts already.

00:07:04.213 --> 00:07:06.582
Then it could be Eun Byul.

00:07:06.583 --> 00:07:08.752
- Finally.
- It was Eun Byul.

00:07:08.753 --> 00:07:10.083
Is it really Eun Byul?

00:07:10.993 --> 00:07:13.353
But Eun Byul and I haven't talked yet.

00:07:13.923 --> 00:07:17.062
I think the one who voted for the First Impression Selection...

00:07:17.063 --> 00:07:19.063
and Attraction Selection is the same.

00:07:19.233 --> 00:07:21.403
I'm not entirely sure if it's Si Woo,

00:07:21.633 --> 00:07:23.062
but I'm sure it's the same person.

00:07:23.063 --> 00:07:24.772
Either way, it's 1 of the 2.

00:07:24.773 --> 00:07:26.672
Wouldn't you get a feeling...

00:07:26.673 --> 00:07:28.803
for who it is if you ask one of them?

00:07:30.373 --> 00:07:32.942
- He's right.
- Yes, just ask upfront.

00:07:32.943 --> 00:07:34.512
- Ask in person?
- Yes.

00:07:34.513 --> 00:07:36.512
- Yoon Hoo is giving him advice.
- He's like a coach.

00:07:36.513 --> 00:07:37.653
Totally.

00:07:39.613 --> 00:07:42.553
(Meanwhile, Eun Byul is doing the dishes by herself.)

00:07:45.123 --> 00:07:46.692
Here he is. Jae Seung is here.

00:07:46.693 --> 00:07:48.463
- Maybe he's going to ask her.
- No, it's just...

00:07:50.323 --> 00:07:52.163
(Glancing)

00:07:52.793 --> 00:07:57.003
(Jae Seung sits in front of Eun Byul.)

00:07:57.803 --> 00:08:02.173
(It's slightly awkward as it's their first time being alone.)

00:08:04.573 --> 00:08:06.112
Can I ask you something?

00:08:06.113 --> 00:08:07.813
We voted twice so far, right?

00:08:09.043 --> 00:08:10.643
- Right.
- He's going to ask.

00:08:11.583 --> 00:08:13.412
- Hold on.
- What is it?

00:08:13.413 --> 00:08:15.482
- I won't ask.
- No, go ahead.

00:08:15.483 --> 00:08:17.122
- I don't have to answer, right?
- No.

00:08:17.123 --> 00:08:18.353
Let me hear the question first.

00:08:19.093 --> 00:08:21.163
Did you vote for the same person for both?

00:08:24.763 --> 00:08:25.793
Yes.

00:08:26.333 --> 00:08:27.503
Really?

00:08:28.633 --> 00:08:31.773
(Eun Byul chose Jae Seung for both.)

00:08:34.203 --> 00:08:36.843
Honestly, when I heard her answer,

00:08:36.873 --> 00:08:40.782
I was totally convinced that both votes were...

00:08:40.783 --> 00:08:42.143
from Eun Byul.

00:08:43.543 --> 00:08:44.553
Wait.

00:08:45.283 --> 00:08:46.682
(Jae Seung finally found out the truth.)

00:08:46.683 --> 00:08:48.422
Jae Seung has found out.

00:08:48.423 --> 00:08:50.083
"I've got it mixed up."

00:08:50.123 --> 00:08:51.653
"It was Eun Byul, not Si Woo."

00:08:53.153 --> 00:08:54.992
You're that type, right?

00:08:54.993 --> 00:08:57.092
- Who approaches...
- Me?

00:08:57.093 --> 00:08:58.963
I like a girl who has feelings for me.

00:09:00.293 --> 00:09:01.463
I see.

00:09:07.333 --> 00:09:09.942
Talking when it's just the two of us...

00:09:09.943 --> 00:09:11.212
- Right?
- is really...

00:09:11.213 --> 00:09:13.043
There isn't much to talk about with the others around.

00:09:13.843 --> 00:09:17.043
Right. Jae Seung asked Si Woo out on a date,

00:09:17.183 --> 00:09:18.312
- Right.
- but he's getting to know...

00:09:18.313 --> 00:09:19.413
Eun Byul more.

00:09:19.583 --> 00:09:22.552
- Out of the things Jae Seung said, - Yes?

00:09:22.553 --> 00:09:25.722
What I found weird was...

00:09:25.723 --> 00:09:29.392
He said something like, "I like a girl..."

00:09:29.393 --> 00:09:30.992
- "who has feelings for me." - Right.

00:09:30.993 --> 00:09:32.563
- What about it?
- Listen.

00:09:32.693 --> 00:09:35.732
That feeling is closer to appreciation than a crush.

00:09:35.733 --> 00:09:36.802
No.

00:09:36.803 --> 00:09:38.202
"Thank you for being interested in me."

00:09:38.203 --> 00:09:40.272
- Nam Jung, what's love?
- What?

00:09:40.273 --> 00:09:42.443
What's love? Tell me.

00:09:43.543 --> 00:09:45.112
Si Woo is already a goner.

00:09:45.113 --> 00:09:46.743
She's not getting any votes.

00:09:47.173 --> 00:09:49.282
At least we're sitting far apart.

00:09:49.283 --> 00:09:51.713
Everyone is interested in Yu Bin now.

00:09:51.983 --> 00:09:53.882
It'd be great if he changed his date right then and there.

00:09:53.883 --> 00:09:56.253
- That's impossible.
- As a dad...

00:09:56.383 --> 00:09:59.153
He's already lost his chance.

00:09:59.323 --> 00:10:02.462
Moon Sik thinks Jae Seung will have a change of heart.

00:10:02.463 --> 00:10:03.522
I'm anxious.

00:10:03.523 --> 00:10:05.632
The date with Si Woo might turn out weirdly.

00:10:05.633 --> 00:10:06.692
- Totally.
- Yes.

00:10:06.693 --> 00:10:07.732
What will happen?

00:10:07.733 --> 00:10:11.073
(Si Woo and Eun Byul)

00:10:11.803 --> 00:10:16.803
(Si Woo is deep in thought alone.)

00:10:19.043 --> 00:10:22.413
Will Hee Dong be alone for the whole day?

00:10:23.543 --> 00:10:25.282
We should ask...

00:10:25.283 --> 00:10:28.053
- if he'll be alone.
- If he's staying at home alone?

00:10:30.023 --> 00:10:31.892
- Why are you sighing?
- Seriously,

00:10:31.893 --> 00:10:34.792
I'm really bad at things like this.

00:10:34.793 --> 00:10:37.193
It feels really strange.

00:10:41.363 --> 00:10:42.903
Honestly...

00:10:45.003 --> 00:10:46.672
At first, I thought...

00:10:46.673 --> 00:10:50.073
how nice it'd be if Hee Dong had asked me out.

00:10:51.813 --> 00:10:56.242
But it must've been half feeling bad and half curiosity.

00:10:56.243 --> 00:10:58.453
He might not have chosen anyone on purpose...

00:10:59.183 --> 00:11:00.353
or...

00:11:01.123 --> 00:11:03.583
might have missed the opportunity.

00:11:07.153 --> 00:11:09.263
I'll go and check.

00:11:13.393 --> 00:11:17.203
(She checks Hee Dong's room.)

00:11:18.133 --> 00:11:20.973
(He's not in his room either.)

00:11:21.873 --> 00:11:24.643
(He's getting ready for his date in Hoo's room.)

00:11:25.413 --> 00:11:27.143
(Peeking)

00:11:31.713 --> 00:11:33.853
(Peeking again)

00:11:36.783 --> 00:11:39.093
(Stopping)

00:11:44.163 --> 00:11:45.532
It looks like she's going to write the letter.

00:11:45.533 --> 00:11:46.533
- The Letter Room?
- To the Letter Room?

00:11:46.534 --> 00:11:47.663
To the Letter Room.

00:11:47.803 --> 00:11:49.533
But her date is coming up soon.

00:11:49.733 --> 00:11:51.032
She came to the Letter Room right before her date?

00:11:51.033 --> 00:11:54.543
(Si Woo visited the Letter Room before her date.)

00:11:59.043 --> 00:12:02.042
(Sighing)

00:12:02.043 --> 00:12:03.583
I don't know what to do.

00:12:06.153 --> 00:12:07.413
What do I do?

00:12:15.193 --> 00:12:19.993
(What's her decision after a long deliberation?)

00:12:20.771 --> 00:12:23.710
(Sighing)

00:12:23.711 --> 00:12:25.381
I don't know what to do.

00:12:27.951 --> 00:12:29.251
What do I do?

00:12:45.631 --> 00:12:49.941
(She decided to sit down.)

00:12:54.381 --> 00:12:57.381
(To Hee Dong)

00:13:06.751 --> 00:13:12.861
(Good morning!)

00:13:13.461 --> 00:13:19.330
(If you're not going on a date...)

00:13:19.331 --> 00:13:24.810
(and staying at home by yourself today, )

00:13:24.811 --> 00:13:28.440
(let's hang out next time!)

00:13:28.441 --> 00:13:32.410
(I don't know if you like hanging out, though.)

00:13:32.411 --> 00:13:33.610
(Laughing)

00:13:33.611 --> 00:13:35.250
(Anyway, )

00:13:35.251 --> 00:13:42.990
(have another great day.)

00:13:42.991 --> 00:13:50.530
(Let's have a chat next time.)

00:13:50.531 --> 00:13:58.311
(Good luck!)

00:14:04.241 --> 00:14:06.880
(She wrote a letter, )

00:14:06.881 --> 00:14:10.021
(worried that he'd be staying at home.)

00:14:18.961 --> 00:14:21.961
(You Hee Dong)

00:14:28.501 --> 00:14:32.371
(She leaves after putting her heartfelt letter in.)

00:14:33.341 --> 00:14:37.181
(Will her letter come through to Hee Dong?)

00:14:40.281 --> 00:14:41.681
When Hee Dong reads it,

00:14:41.881 --> 00:14:43.951
I'm sure his heart will melt.

00:14:44.421 --> 00:14:46.050
- Goodness.
- Right now, Hee Dong is...

00:14:46.051 --> 00:14:48.191
(Hee Dong's dad smiles, seeing how genuine Si Woo is.)

00:14:48.891 --> 00:14:50.790
Now, the problem is...

00:14:50.791 --> 00:14:52.660
when Hee Dong reads the letter.

00:14:52.661 --> 00:14:55.501
Will he read it before meeting the female latecomer...

00:14:55.931 --> 00:14:59.030
or after going on a date with her?

00:14:59.031 --> 00:15:00.500
- That will be important.
- Right.

00:15:00.501 --> 00:15:03.940
Jae Seung and Si Woo are having second thoughts...

00:15:03.941 --> 00:15:05.511
before their date.

00:15:05.671 --> 00:15:07.641
