01:07:08.369 --> 01:07:10.539
- Do you want to try it on now?
- Yes.

01:07:24.559 --> 01:07:25.659
Shall I help you with it?

01:07:27.019 --> 01:07:28.059
Yes.

01:07:28.359 --> 01:07:29.629
That's right!

01:07:30.389 --> 01:07:32.459
Is this the final episode of a drama?

01:07:32.499 --> 01:07:34.668
I can't believe Hee Dong!

01:07:34.669 --> 01:07:35.899
(Hee Dong's flirting is sweeter than a drama.)

01:07:56.889 --> 01:07:59.919
My heart fluttered when he helped me with the necklace.

01:08:06.259 --> 01:08:08.999
Since it was my first time putting a necklace on a woman,

01:08:09.299 --> 01:08:10.829
I was nervous.

01:08:17.069 --> 01:08:19.239
- All done.
- Thank you.

01:08:20.239 --> 01:08:21.309
How do I look?

01:08:24.649 --> 01:08:26.378
- It's pretty.
- It's pretty.

01:08:26.379 --> 01:08:27.749
My goodness.

01:08:28.889 --> 01:08:30.549
- Does it look good on me?
- It looks good on you.

01:08:30.649 --> 01:08:32.319
- Really?
- You're like that teddy bear.

01:08:32.659 --> 01:08:34.989
I'll take out the necklace I was wearing...

01:08:35.089 --> 01:08:36.589
- later.
- Okay.

01:08:38.259 --> 01:08:39.659
I'll wear this instead.

01:08:41.429 --> 01:08:42.828
Please wear it.

01:08:42.829 --> 01:08:44.838
- I'll wear it for real.
- Okay.

01:08:44.839 --> 01:08:46.369
I have two necklaces now.

01:08:48.569 --> 01:08:49.609
Thank you.

01:08:51.339 --> 01:08:53.609
They resemble each other a bit.

01:08:54.979 --> 01:08:56.678
You did a good job of making Shiro.

01:08:56.679 --> 01:08:57.778
- It's cute, right?
- Yes.

01:08:57.779 --> 01:08:59.849
(Hee Dong's romantic event brings them closer.)

01:09:01.419 --> 01:09:03.288
- He had one shot.
- That's right.

01:09:03.289 --> 01:09:04.858
I think that was your strategy.

01:09:04.859 --> 01:09:07.419
- No. I swear there was nothing.
- My goodness.

01:09:07.819 --> 01:09:09.558
I get Seo Yoon a lot of gifts...

01:09:09.559 --> 01:09:10.758
and buy her a lot.

01:09:10.759 --> 01:09:12.158
She likes it more than the gifts from me.

01:09:12.159 --> 01:09:13.398
- Does she?
- She looks...

01:09:13.399 --> 01:09:14.498
- Different?
- Yes.

01:09:14.499 --> 01:09:15.769
I approve.

01:09:16.529 --> 01:09:17.628
Right now,

01:09:17.629 --> 01:09:19.998
Don't you hear someone moaning?

01:09:19.999 --> 01:09:20.999
My goodness.

01:09:21.000 --> 01:09:22.608
Will he even read Si Woo's letter?

01:09:22.609 --> 01:09:23.769
- What's she going to do?
- Right?

01:09:23.869 --> 01:09:25.979
But they've met only recently.

01:09:26.079 --> 01:09:28.848
But one family is on fire.

01:09:28.849 --> 01:09:30.549
Which family? Si Woo's family?

01:09:30.909 --> 01:09:31.979
Yes.

01:09:32.279 --> 01:09:35.019
I'm not on fire, but I'm sweating.

01:09:39.089 --> 01:09:43.389
(The night draws.)

01:09:44.029 --> 01:09:46.098
- Today, time...
- Time flew, right?

01:09:46.099 --> 01:09:47.129
Yes.

01:09:47.229 --> 01:09:49.429
It's so different from yesterday.

01:09:53.369 --> 01:09:55.609
- Do you like dogs?
- I like dogs.

01:09:56.409 --> 01:09:57.808
I love dogs.

01:09:57.809 --> 01:09:58.879
- Really?
- Yes.

01:09:59.079 --> 01:10:01.478
- I have a dog.
- Me too.

01:10:01.479 --> 01:10:02.579
- You do?
- Yes.

01:10:03.579 --> 01:10:05.278
- I said it first.
- What?

01:10:05.279 --> 01:10:07.618
- You're copying me.
- I'm not.

01:10:07.619 --> 01:10:08.918
You're copying me so much.

01:10:08.919 --> 01:10:11.389
(You're copying me so much.)

01:10:11.919 --> 01:10:14.019
Do you prefer dogs over cats?

01:10:14.889 --> 01:10:16.258
I prefer dogs over cats,

01:10:16.259 --> 01:10:17.958
- but I love cats, too.
- Really?

01:10:17.959 --> 01:10:19.899
I love cats so much.

01:10:20.499 --> 01:10:23.369
It's a shame that I'm allergic to their hair.

01:10:23.899 --> 01:10:24.938
Me too.

01:10:24.939 --> 01:10:27.068
(They keep finding something in common.)

01:10:27.069 --> 01:10:28.139
No way.

01:10:28.739 --> 01:10:31.208
(What's going on?)

01:10:31.209 --> 01:10:34.278
Now I get why they received zero votes.

01:10:34.279 --> 01:10:35.678
- That makes sense.
- Right.

01:10:35.679 --> 01:10:38.048
- For them to meet?
- Yes.

01:10:38.049 --> 01:10:39.579
It's a fateful encounter.

01:10:42.589 --> 01:10:46.758
Now that we've spent a day together,

01:10:46.759 --> 01:10:48.089
- Right?
- I feel closer.

01:10:48.689 --> 01:10:52.228
I normally don't talk much,

01:10:52.229 --> 01:10:54.159
- Okay.
- but when we were together,

01:10:54.329 --> 01:10:55.728
I was able to...

01:10:55.729 --> 01:10:58.169
- Really?
- talk a lot.

01:11:02.609 --> 01:11:03.939
It might get hard now.

01:11:05.679 --> 01:11:08.479
You'll have to put up with my jokes.

01:11:09.309 --> 01:11:10.879
I'm ready.

01:11:12.479 --> 01:11:13.719
(Smiling)

01:11:15.019 --> 01:11:16.589
You can feel free.

01:11:18.319 --> 01:11:20.119
You're already putting up with my jokes.

01:11:22.029 --> 01:11:23.388
- Did you already make jokes?
- What?

01:11:23.389 --> 01:11:27.229
(The two are making more and more jokes.)

01:11:29.399 --> 01:11:32.739
(And these two are breathtakingly quiet.)

01:11:33.439 --> 01:11:36.039
- My goodness.
- His father is appearing.

01:11:36.269 --> 01:11:38.138
- It's profound.
- Everyone, let's cheer up.

01:11:38.139 --> 01:11:40.378
- Let's all cheer up.
- Jae Seung.

01:11:40.379 --> 01:11:41.548
Let's cheer up.

01:11:41.549 --> 01:11:42.809
(Already getting anxious)

01:11:42.949 --> 01:11:44.749
What did you talk about with Hee Dong yesterday?

01:11:45.719 --> 01:11:47.079
Are they still talking about Hee Dong?

01:11:48.619 --> 01:11:51.559
We went straight to bed. We were too tired.

01:11:54.789 --> 01:11:56.089
(Sighing)

01:11:56.429 --> 01:11:57.728
(Hee Dong's roommate isn't very helpful...)

01:11:57.729 --> 01:11:59.128
(when Si Woo is curious about Hee Dong.)

01:11:59.129 --> 01:12:01.029
What's tormenting you?

01:12:03.229 --> 01:12:04.839
I don't know what I want either.

01:12:07.399 --> 01:12:08.809
You can just talk to him...

01:12:09.109 --> 01:12:12.739
when he's sitting on the couch.

01:12:14.539 --> 01:12:16.108
(His advice isn't very helpful either.)

01:12:16.109 --> 01:12:17.109
Okay.

01:12:21.449 --> 01:12:23.289
What is Eun Byul like?

01:12:24.619 --> 01:12:25.819
(Smirking)

01:12:26.889 --> 01:12:30.259
Eun Byul is nice to everyone.

01:12:30.529 --> 01:12:32.628
Actually, she's not much different.

01:12:32.629 --> 01:12:33.958
- Really?
- What you see is everything.

01:12:33.959 --> 01:12:35.899
- Does she talk a lot in the room?
- No.

01:12:36.369 --> 01:12:37.429
Really?

01:12:37.829 --> 01:12:40.099
She seems very kind.

01:12:40.899 --> 01:12:41.939
Really?

01:12:43.509 --> 01:12:44.639
She sounds like an angel.

01:12:46.079 --> 01:12:47.479
(Chuckling)

01:12:48.749 --> 01:12:49.879
Wait a minute.

01:12:50.009 --> 01:12:51.748
- He's talking about Eun Byul.
- Eun Byul...

01:12:51.749 --> 01:12:53.979
- The two are acting weird.
- Eun Byul...

01:12:54.219 --> 01:12:55.288
- My goodness.
- Jae Seung.

01:12:55.289 --> 01:12:56.618
- Why would he talk to her about it?
- Gosh.

01:12:56.619 --> 01:12:58.458
He's not hiding it anymore.

01:12:58.459 --> 01:13:00.119
Regardless of who's in front of him.

01:13:01.059 --> 01:13:02.258
He's transferred.

01:13:02.259 --> 01:13:03.289
(Bitter)

01:13:03.589 --> 01:13:05.699
- I think he's given up on Si Woo.
- Yes.

01:13:05.999 --> 01:13:08.969
It's not that Si Woo doesn't care about Hee Dong,

01:13:09.169 --> 01:13:12.538
but she wants Jae Seung to entertain her.

01:13:12.539 --> 01:13:15.239
But he keeps talking about Eun Byul and other people...

01:13:15.339 --> 01:13:17.209
or who picked him.

01:13:17.409 --> 01:13:19.078
He's only being calculative.

01:13:19.079 --> 01:13:20.439
- So Jae Seung is the problem?
- Yes.

01:13:20.579 --> 01:13:22.879
Si Woo talked about Hee Dong first.

01:13:23.509 --> 01:13:24.509
- What?
- So Si Woo is the problem?

01:13:24.510 --> 01:13:26.748
Jae Seung should've induced her.

01:13:26.749 --> 01:13:29.318
Si Woo keeps staring outside.

01:13:29.319 --> 01:13:32.118
He should've led her.

01:13:32.119 --> 01:13:33.458
He's not the host. Why would he lead her?

01:13:33.459 --> 01:13:34.758
Maybe they weren't interested in each other.

01:13:34.759 --> 01:13:36.258
And they somehow got to meet. Is that it?

01:13:36.259 --> 01:13:37.588
It's a mess.

01:13:37.589 --> 01:13:38.629
- Is it?
- Yes, it is.

01:13:38.759 --> 01:13:41.129
He should've made her look at him.

01:13:41.499 --> 01:13:42.729
Let's transfer.

01:13:43.229 --> 01:13:44.969
Forget about being consistent.

01:13:45.139 --> 01:13:46.139
Transfer to someone else.

01:13:46.140 --> 01:13:48.569
- Sir, is that okay?
- Of course, it's okay.

01:13:48.639 --> 01:13:49.969
He's about to die.

01:13:50.209 --> 01:13:51.578
Park Nam Jung and Lee Moon Sik can...

01:13:51.579 --> 01:13:53.778
go on separate ways.

01:13:53.779 --> 01:13:56.479
It can't get any worse. This is a complete mess.

01:13:58.619 --> 01:13:59.878
What do you think of Eun Byul?

01:13:59.879 --> 01:14:02.489
Eun Byul? She's very kind and sweet.

01:14:04.619 --> 01:14:06.619
(Shy)

01:14:06.859 --> 01:14:07.988
I couldn't wait...

01:14:07.989 --> 01:14:11.659
to get home and talk to Eun Byul.

01:14:11.829 --> 01:14:12.959
That's what I was thinking.

01:14:13.959 --> 01:14:16.268
Things have changed a lot for Eun Byul.

01:14:16.269 --> 01:14:17.329
Right.

01:14:18.099 --> 01:14:20.438
(Jae Seung and Si Woo get home.)

01:14:20.439 --> 01:14:21.539
- It's cold.
- Oh, what?

01:14:21.909 --> 01:14:23.009
Hello.

01:14:25.539 --> 01:14:26.979
Hello.

01:14:28.009 --> 01:14:29.649
Did you have a good time?

01:14:31.679 --> 01:14:32.819
(Glancing)

01:14:34.219 --> 01:14:36.289
Where is Jae Hyuk?

01:14:36.489 --> 01:14:38.019
- Is he in the room?
- He's in the room.

01:14:38.089 --> 01:14:40.619
- Is it only the two of you?
- Yes, we're the first to get home.

01:14:40.819 --> 01:14:42.789
- You're early.
- Did you go out?

01:14:42.989 --> 01:14:44.458
- We came home...
- What did you do?

01:14:44.459 --> 01:14:46.528
Like less than ten minutes ago.

01:14:46.529 --> 01:14:47.899
- Us?
- Ten minutes?

01:14:48.029 --> 01:14:49.229
Did you eat?

01:14:49.469 --> 01:14:52.039
Yes, we had late lunch.

01:14:52.499 --> 01:14:55.738
(Waiting for his chance to talk to her again)

01:14:55.739 --> 01:14:57.308
We had brunch.

01:14:57.309 --> 01:14:58.938
Brunch? Where did you go?

01:14:58.939 --> 01:15:02.078
We had it around 3pm.

01:15:02.079 --> 01:15:04.979
We had very late lunch.

01:15:05.119 --> 01:15:06.218
(The door closed even before he could stop them.)

01:15:06.219 --> 01:15:07.349
Gosh, it hurts.

01:15:10.689 --> 01:15:15.259
(He decides to wait for his next chance.)

01:15:16.459 --> 01:15:18.599
Did you have something good?

01:15:18.829 --> 01:15:21.059
- Raw fish.
- I'm jealous.

01:15:23.029 --> 01:15:24.169
How was it?

01:15:25.199 --> 01:15:26.268
- It was good.
- It was good?

01:15:26.269 --> 01:15:27.799
Yes. How was it?

01:15:28.469 --> 01:15:30.968
I saw every side of him...

01:15:30.969 --> 01:15:33.578
that I hadn't seen.

01:15:33.579 --> 01:15:34.679
Really?

01:15:35.309 --> 01:15:37.609
(Laughing)

01:15:38.349 --> 01:15:39.479
It's over now.

01:15:40.179 --> 01:15:41.619
What's that supposed to mean?

01:15:41.789 --> 01:15:43.618
- It's over now.
- She saw every side of him.

01:15:43.619 --> 01:15:45.418
There's hardly a chance between Si Woo and Jae Seung.

01:15:45.419 --> 01:15:46.658
What's that supposed to mean?

01:15:46.659 --> 01:15:48.118
- She saw every side of him?
- Every side of him.

01:15:48.119 --> 01:15:49.858
That has a lot of meanings.

01:15:49.859 --> 01:15:51.229
- Let's keep watching.
- Yes.

01:15:51.389 --> 01:15:52.559
- That's hilarious.
- Gosh.

01:15:54.299 --> 01:15:55.469
Be honest with me.

01:15:56.429 --> 01:15:57.569
How do you feel?

01:15:57.699 --> 01:15:59.269
- Me?
- How do you feel about him?

01:16:01.069 --> 01:16:02.969
- It wasn't so bad.
- No?

01:16:03.839 --> 01:16:05.839
I liked it. I had a good time.

01:16:06.079 --> 01:16:07.109
- You did?
- Yes.

01:16:07.209 --> 01:16:09.179
Any change in mind?

01:16:11.409 --> 01:16:12.818
- I'm not sure.
- You're not sure?

01:16:12.819 --> 01:16:13.819
No.

01:16:16.649 --> 01:16:19.388
(Meanwhile, Jae Hyuk's in the living room.)

01:16:19.389 --> 01:16:20.658
(And Jae Seung as well.)

01:16:20.659 --> 01:16:22.228
- Did you have a good time?
- Yes.

01:16:22.229 --> 01:16:24.189
I had such a great time. What about you?

01:16:25.359 --> 01:16:28.729
Me? When we were having a meal alone,

01:16:29.099 --> 01:16:31.299
- I'm not much of a smooth talker.
- Okay.

01:16:31.529 --> 01:16:34.168
- And Si Woo led me.
- She led you?

01:16:34.169 --> 01:16:35.869
It was nice of her.

01:16:38.039 --> 01:16:40.508
- What did you eat?
- We had raw fish.

01:16:40.509 --> 01:16:41.748
- Really? Did you have raw fish?
- Yes.

01:16:41.749 --> 01:16:43.809
- Did you go there?
- Yes. What did you have?

01:16:44.079 --> 01:16:45.379
We went to a brunch cafe.

01:16:48.119 --> 01:16:49.618
(Glancing)

01:16:49.619 --> 01:16:52.388
Doesn't he look like he's waiting for Eun Byul?

01:16:52.389 --> 01:16:53.759
- Yes.
- Right?

01:16:55.489 --> 01:16:57.459
Did you do anything other than going to a cafe?

01:16:57.729 --> 01:17:00.499
We went to some station,

01:17:01.159 --> 01:17:03.369
and we... Oh, do you want me to take a picture of you with it?

01:17:03.999 --> 01:17:05.569
What is that?

01:17:05.769 --> 01:17:07.698
The one that prints right away.

01:17:07.699 --> 01:17:09.068
- Oh, really?
- Polaroid.

01:17:09.069 --> 01:17:10.568
Yes. Let me take pictures of you.

01:17:10.569 --> 01:17:12.708
(It's a good chance to appeal to Eun Byul.)

01:17:12.709 --> 01:17:13.739
Awesome.

01:17:14.009 --> 01:17:15.449
Why don't you take a picture of making a fire?

01:17:16.709 --> 01:17:17.948
What?

01:17:17.949 --> 01:17:19.119
(Eun Byul and Jae Hyuk look close.)

01:17:20.049 --> 01:17:21.419
(Exclaiming)

01:17:22.019 --> 01:17:23.689
Or do you want to sit here?

01:17:26.089 --> 01:17:27.519
What should we do to get a good picture of you?

01:17:32.299 --> 01:17:33.799
Well...

01:17:36.029 --> 01:17:37.369
- Do you want to join me?
- Do you want to take it together?

01:17:37.829 --> 01:17:39.399
It's awkward by myself.

01:17:39.899 --> 01:17:41.068
- Do you want to join me?
- Do you want to take it together?

01:17:41.069 --> 01:17:42.669
(Moving back)

01:17:43.609 --> 01:17:44.838
"Do you want to join me?"

01:17:44.839 --> 01:17:46.339
Hey.

01:17:46.709 --> 01:17:48.079
No. Don't do that.

01:17:49.309 --> 01:17:51.109
Jae Seung is very kind.

01:17:51.309 --> 01:17:52.318
That makes no sense.

01:17:52.319 --> 01:17:55.319
Why would he... That's off side.

01:17:56.089 --> 01:17:57.849
- We need to raise the flag.
- Yes.

01:17:59.459 --> 01:18:01.189
- Do you want to join me?
- Do you want to take it together?

01:18:01.929 --> 01:18:03.429
It's awkward by myself.

01:18:04.289 --> 01:18:06.259
- Let's try making a fire.
- How?

01:18:06.329 --> 01:18:08.358
- Wait.
- Try opening it.

01:18:08.359 --> 01:18:09.429
- Wait.
- Like this?

01:18:09.969 --> 01:18:11.599
- Is this right?
- That's good.

01:18:13.399 --> 01:18:15.209
Jae Seung is not a photographer.

01:18:16.869 --> 01:18:18.479
- Is this right?
- That's good.

01:18:21.509 --> 01:18:23.848
Hold this, and I'll hold the broom.

01:18:23.849 --> 01:18:25.318
(Getting ready to take a picture...)

01:18:25.319 --> 01:18:27.549
(of the two who look harmonious)

01:18:28.379 --> 01:18:30.188
No, just stay still.

01:18:30.189 --> 01:18:31.289
I'll stay still.

01:18:32.059 --> 01:18:34.789
What's he doing? You're not a guide.

01:18:35.729 --> 01:18:38.259
It's not Jae Seung's lucky day.

01:18:38.599 --> 01:18:40.259
I look awkward.

01:18:41.199 --> 01:18:43.798
I'll leave it here. You need to wait for the picture to appear.

01:18:43.799 --> 01:18:44.929
- Okay.
- Thank you.

01:18:46.039 --> 01:18:47.939
We should've tried to look nicer.

01:18:48.339 --> 01:18:49.368
What kind of concept was that?

01:18:49.369 --> 01:18:51.539
I don't think it was taken properly.

01:18:53.979 --> 01:18:56.008
I wasn't planning to take it together with her.

01:18:56.009 --> 01:18:57.449
I was only going to take a picture of her alone.

01:18:57.949 --> 01:18:59.979
Then she asked him to join the picture.

01:19:00.319 --> 01:19:01.549
So I took a picture of them together.

01:19:04.849 --> 01:19:08.929
(Jae Hyuk who was a step ahead got to take a picture with her.)

01:19:09.529 --> 01:19:12.299
It's starting to appear. It looks funny.

01:19:16.869 --> 01:19:19.238
I could see that Eun Byul and Jae Hyuk...

01:19:19.239 --> 01:19:20.439
returned very close.

01:19:21.599 --> 01:19:24.709
I wondered if I had a chance...

01:19:24.869 --> 01:19:26.009
between them.

01:19:28.379 --> 01:19:30.708
It's romantic.

01:19:30.709 --> 01:19:32.978
(He keeps missing his chance with Eun Byul.)

01:19:32.979 --> 01:19:34.848
There's no gap.

01:19:34.849 --> 01:19:37.288
Eun Byul became very close to Jae Hyuk.

01:19:37.289 --> 01:19:38.448
- They became close.
- Yes.

01:19:38.449 --> 01:19:39.988
- They understand each other.
- They do.

01:19:39.989 --> 01:19:43.389
- Gosh.
- Jae Seung must be disturbed.

01:19:44.759 --> 01:19:48.129
(Meanwhile, Yoon Hoo and Yu Bin return.)

01:19:52.639 --> 01:19:54.168
- We're back.
- Hello.

01:19:54.169 --> 01:19:55.409
You're back.

01:19:59.339 --> 01:20:01.779
(They're eating something.)

01:20:01.879 --> 01:20:03.709
- What are you eating?
- Apollo?

01:20:03.909 --> 01:20:04.979
Popeye.

01:20:05.649 --> 01:20:07.119
What? Apollo.

01:20:07.319 --> 01:20:09.289
(Dashing to the snack)

01:20:13.589 --> 01:20:14.689
He has to relieve his hangover.

01:20:15.189 --> 01:20:16.189
(Laughing)

01:20:16.190 --> 01:20:17.728
Don't you think you're eating too fast?

01:20:17.729 --> 01:20:19.698
(Having a candy in front of his crush)

01:20:19.699 --> 01:20:20.928
(Struggling)

01:20:20.929 --> 01:20:21.969
That's...

01:20:23.529 --> 01:20:25.299
Yoon Hoo is such a good singer.

01:20:26.069 --> 01:20:27.839
(Curious)

01:20:29.009 --> 01:20:30.339
He liked it since he was a child.

01:20:31.609 --> 01:20:33.409
I guess he nailed it at karaoke.

01:20:34.709 --> 01:20:35.879
(Nodding)

01:20:36.209 --> 01:20:38.509
That reminds me of the time when he had jjajang ramyeon.

01:20:38.979 --> 01:20:40.819
- He must've been hungry.
- Yes.

01:20:41.379 --> 01:20:42.789
Do you want me to microwave some fried rice for you?

01:20:43.389 --> 01:20:45.049
- Can I?
- Of course.

01:20:46.459 --> 01:20:48.219
- Then I want it.
- I'll get it for you.

01:20:50.229 --> 01:20:52.529
- Yes.
- You didn't even get changed.

01:20:52.699 --> 01:20:54.999
- The two get along.
- Like a couple.

01:20:55.529 --> 01:20:57.529
They look like a newlywed couple.

01:20:58.229 --> 01:21:00.099
They look like...

01:21:00.299 --> 01:21:02.738
- They look like they're married.
- They do.

01:21:02.739 --> 01:21:04.508
She looks like she's cooking for him after getting home.

01:21:04.509 --> 01:21:05.579
Exactly.

01:21:06.579 --> 01:21:08.109
Gosh. I'm so happy.

01:21:09.079 --> 01:21:10.508
- Thank you for the food.
- Sure.

01:21:10.509 --> 01:21:11.609
(Nom)

01:21:12.119 --> 01:21:13.419
(Overwhelmed)

01:21:14.049 --> 01:21:16.449
This is so much better than the grilled clams.

01:21:16.849 --> 01:21:18.489
- No way.
- I mean it.

01:21:18.659 --> 01:21:20.819
I'm happy that you enjoy it.

01:21:21.119 --> 01:21:23.289
That place looks like Yoon Hoo's.

01:21:23.459 --> 01:21:25.188
It's like Yoon Hoo's having guests in his house.

01:21:25.189 --> 01:21:26.829
(They act like a newlywed couple.)

01:21:29.799 --> 01:21:31.268
Aren't you hungry?

01:21:31.269 --> 01:21:33.698
(Meanwhile, Si Woo and Jae Seung are in the living room.)

01:21:33.699 --> 01:21:34.699
A little.

01:21:38.939 --> 01:21:41.179
(Glancing)

01:21:51.319 --> 01:21:53.159
(Glancing)

01:21:53.719 --> 01:21:57.759
(Si Woo keeps staring at the gate.)

01:21:58.959 --> 01:22:00.029
I...

01:22:01.499 --> 01:22:04.299
I just kept thinking.

01:22:06.139 --> 01:22:07.468
What would he be doing?

01:22:07.469 --> 01:22:10.239
(What would Hee Dong be doing?)

01:22:10.709 --> 01:22:13.409
- Oh, Hee Dong.
- Gosh.

01:22:14.979 --> 01:22:16.579
Did he meet another woman?

01:22:17.349 --> 01:22:19.019
Whom is he with?

01:22:20.419 --> 01:22:22.319
I kept thinking about that.

01:22:24.949 --> 01:22:27.519
I was curious about the woman.

01:22:29.659 --> 01:22:31.928
Si Woo knows about the female latecomer.

01:22:31.929 --> 01:22:33.028
Oh, right. She does.

01:22:33.029 --> 01:22:35.899
That's bothering Si Woo.

01:22:38.869 --> 01:22:42.209
(While she's getting more curious about Hee Dong's date, )

01:22:43.869 --> 01:22:47.239
(Hee Dong and Seo Yoon are getting close to home.)

01:22:47.439 --> 01:22:48.639
We're in Pyeongchang.

01:22:49.649 --> 01:22:51.208
(Restless)

01:22:51.209 --> 01:22:52.279
Oh, my gosh.

01:22:54.279 --> 01:22:55.388
(Laughing)

01:22:55.389 --> 01:22:57.649
I wasn't nervous before.

01:23:00.319 --> 01:23:01.619
Let me have some water.

01:23:03.029 --> 01:23:05.288
- She's getting nervous now.
- Yes.

01:23:05.289 --> 01:23:06.859
Because this is her first visit.

01:23:12.139 --> 01:23:13.469
(Sighing)

01:23:13.899 --> 01:23:16.609
I know exactly how that feels.

01:23:17.469 --> 01:23:18.539
It's okay.

01:23:19.109 --> 01:23:20.109
I mean...

01:23:22.849 --> 01:23:23.879
You must be nervous.

01:23:24.309 --> 01:23:25.879
You can hide behind me.

01:23:28.719 --> 01:23:31.449
"Hide behind me." That's short and simple.

01:23:31.949 --> 01:23:33.019
That's cool.

01:23:36.189 --> 01:23:38.089
Anyway, when is he coming home?

01:23:38.899 --> 01:23:39.959
I don't know.

01:23:40.629 --> 01:23:42.098
What if he's not coming back?

01:23:42.099 --> 01:23:43.398
I know. That's what I was thinking.

01:23:43.399 --> 01:23:46.239
- He wouldn't do that though, right?
- He wouldn't.

01:23:50.839 --> 01:23:53.808
Si Woo likes Hee Dong so much.

01:23:53.809 --> 01:23:55.508
Have you ever seen Si Woo like that before?

01:23:55.509 --> 01:23:58.879
Revealing her emotions and getting heartrending?

01:23:59.179 --> 01:24:00.179
- And waiting?
- No.

01:24:00.180 --> 01:24:02.788
I don't have a lot of chances to see that at home.

01:24:02.789 --> 01:24:05.318
I think this is the first time...

01:24:05.319 --> 01:24:08.759
to see Si Woo's expressions of waiting someone...

01:24:08.929 --> 01:24:11.288
in detail.

01:24:11.289 --> 01:24:13.559
I know. She's normally shrewd.

01:24:13.729 --> 01:24:16.028
- She's emotionally wavered.
- That's true.

01:24:16.029 --> 01:24:18.768
Si Woo is...

01:24:18.769 --> 01:24:20.768
expressing her emotions a lot.

01:24:20.769 --> 01:24:21.838
- Right?
- Yes.

01:24:21.839 --> 01:24:22.839
(Her dad is proud of her yet feeling sad.)

01:24:24.209 --> 01:24:25.368
The newbie is...

01:24:25.369 --> 01:24:27.309
(Hee Dong and Seo Yoon reach the house.)

01:24:28.039 --> 01:24:30.049
- They're coming.
- Here we go.

01:24:30.479 --> 01:24:31.649
They're here.

01:24:32.879 --> 01:24:34.549
I am really here.

01:24:36.219 --> 01:24:37.319
Oh, wait.

01:24:37.689 --> 01:24:39.318
Do you need some time before going in?

01:24:39.319 --> 01:24:41.759
Yes, I need some time... Gosh, you can see inside.

01:24:41.959 --> 01:24:43.829
You can't see it here yet.

01:24:44.289 --> 01:24:45.799
I can see them.

01:24:47.229 --> 01:24:49.869
(Everyone's in the living room.)

01:24:50.329 --> 01:24:51.868
I guess we're pretty good.

01:24:51.869 --> 01:24:53.339
(The one who is cluless)

01:24:54.869 --> 01:24:57.739
(The one who's blushing for some reason)

01:24:58.369 --> 01:25:01.009
(And the one who's very nervous)

01:25:01.579 --> 01:25:03.078
(How will their first encounter go with Seo Yoon?)

01:25:03.079 --> 01:25:04.179
Do you want to go in first?

01:25:04.449 --> 01:25:06.348
- All right.
- Let me see her face.

01:25:06.349 --> 01:25:08.718
I can't wait to see Si Woo's reaction.

01:25:08.719 --> 01:25:12.259
I can't wait to see the look on Si Woo's face the most.

01:25:15.219 --> 01:25:16.859
- Do you want me to open it first?
- Yes.

01:25:18.759 --> 01:25:22.569
(She hide behinds Hee Dong as they promised.)

01:25:32.939 --> 01:25:34.509
Yoon Hoo.

01:25:34.839 --> 01:25:36.178
Yoon Hoo. What's that look on your face?

01:25:36.179 --> 01:25:38.309
- Yoon Hoo's shocked.
- He's shocked.

01:25:42.519 --> 01:25:44.219
- Put on the slippers here.
- Okay.

01:25:46.419 --> 01:25:50.229
(They hear a conversation by the gate.)

01:25:50.859 --> 01:25:51.859
Are they here?

01:25:52.529 --> 01:25:53.559
The two?

01:25:57.869 --> 01:25:58.899
Oh, my gosh.

01:26:07.079 --> 01:26:09.409
(The footsteps are getting closer.)

01:26:10.909 --> 01:26:13.348
- Hello.
- Hello.

01:26:13.349 --> 01:26:14.649
Hello.

01:26:15.649 --> 01:26:18.049
- Hello.
- Hello.

01:26:18.119 --> 01:26:22.759
(Finally meeting the new resident)

01:26:24.459 --> 01:26:25.529
Hello.

01:26:26.899 --> 01:26:28.899
- Si Woo.
- Si Woo.

01:26:29.069 --> 01:26:31.229
- She looks a bit nervous.
- Yes.

01:26:32.499 --> 01:26:34.369
She's very pretty.

01:26:34.769 --> 01:26:36.509
She looks like a model. She looks elegant.

01:26:36.609 --> 01:26:40.679
Normally, tall guys like tall girls.

01:26:41.579 --> 01:26:45.549
So I think they had a good time.

01:26:47.119 --> 01:26:48.318
(Feeling bad for Si Woo)

01:26:48.319 --> 01:26:49.819
She's forcing herself to smile, but...

01:26:50.219 --> 01:26:52.489
She waited for Hee Dong so much.

01:27:02.059 --> 01:27:03.169
Hello.

01:27:06.869 --> 01:27:08.139
Hello.

01:27:08.269 --> 01:27:09.908
Someone very tall...

01:27:09.909 --> 01:27:12.239
like a model walked in.

01:27:12.539 --> 01:27:15.878
I'm a little worried...

01:27:15.879 --> 01:27:18.679
because I might be compared.

01:27:20.649 --> 01:27:22.749
(Grunting)

01:27:23.319 --> 01:27:26.859
She looked kind of chic.

01:27:27.319 --> 01:27:29.429
I'm curious about what she's like.

01:27:30.189 --> 01:27:32.358
The sons probably want to...

01:27:32.359 --> 01:27:34.228
go on a date with her.

01:27:34.229 --> 01:27:35.558
- Yes.
- Of course.

01:27:35.559 --> 01:27:36.669
- They're curious.
- Yes.

01:27:38.369 --> 01:27:41.238
The atmosphere instantly...

01:27:41.239 --> 01:27:42.338
It's getting strange.

01:27:42.339 --> 01:27:43.639
(The atmosphere instantly became strange.)

01:27:47.179 --> 01:27:49.378
- Hello.
- Hello.

01:27:49.379 --> 01:27:51.579
(All 8 kids finally gathered.)

01:27:52.009 --> 01:27:53.118
What's your name?

01:27:53.119 --> 01:27:54.448
I'm Woo Seo Yoon.

01:27:54.449 --> 01:27:55.789
- Seo Yoon?
- Yes.

01:27:56.449 --> 01:27:57.788
What are your names?

01:27:57.789 --> 01:27:59.819
- I'm Park Si Woo.
- Si Woo?

01:28:00.259 --> 01:28:01.788
I'm Choi Yu Bin.

01:28:01.789 --> 01:28:02.858
Yu Bin.

01:28:02.859 --> 01:28:05.589
- I'm Yoon Hoo.
- I'm Lee Jae Seung.

01:28:05.729 --> 01:28:07.429
- Jae Seung.
- I'm Shin Jae Hyuk.

01:28:07.559 --> 01:28:08.559
Jae Hyuk.

01:28:09.629 --> 01:28:10.869
You haven't forgotten my name, right?

01:28:11.929 --> 01:28:12.969
Hee Dong.

01:28:13.469 --> 01:28:15.338
- I'm Cho Eun Byul.
- Eun Byul.

01:28:15.339 --> 01:28:16.369
Yes.

01:28:18.169 --> 01:28:21.308
(You haven't forgotten my name, right?)

01:28:21.309 --> 01:28:22.848
- He...
- Gosh.

01:28:22.849 --> 01:28:23.949
He makes a move right there.

01:28:24.879 --> 01:28:26.319
He's forgotten about Si Woo.

01:28:26.379 --> 01:28:28.919
Why would he say that there?

01:28:29.589 --> 01:28:31.619
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

01:28:32.249 --> 01:28:33.259
Welcome.

01:28:36.959 --> 01:28:38.959
- Did you make something?
- Yes.

01:28:39.929 --> 01:28:41.028
Did you win it?

01:28:41.029 --> 01:28:42.398
- We made it.
- I see.

01:28:42.399 --> 01:28:44.128
For each other?

01:28:44.129 --> 01:28:45.129
Yes.

01:28:45.130 --> 01:28:47.469
One for ourselves, and the other for each other.

01:28:48.169 --> 01:28:50.169
- Oh, that's cute.
- Awesome.

01:28:53.209 --> 01:28:54.809
- That's really cute.
- It's cute, right?

01:28:55.079 --> 01:28:56.378
Did you decorate it yourself?

01:28:56.379 --> 01:28:57.908
- With what they had.
- With what they had?

01:28:57.909 --> 01:28:59.819
So...

01:29:04.919 --> 01:29:07.719
They made dolls.

01:29:08.259 --> 01:29:10.628
I think they made matching ones...

01:29:10.629 --> 01:29:13.659
by decorating their dolls.

01:29:13.929 --> 01:29:15.029
That's why...

01:29:17.799 --> 01:29:20.739
Why did he have to do that...

01:29:22.169 --> 01:29:25.509
of all things with someone else?

01:29:26.739 --> 01:29:28.778
- Come on.
- It's bothering her.

01:29:28.779 --> 01:29:30.879
It's really bothering her.

01:29:31.649 --> 01:29:34.949
Hee Dong, Si Woo wrote a letter to you.

01:29:35.019 --> 01:29:36.189
Goodness.

01:29:37.519 --> 01:29:39.588
- Dinner?
- We had lunch.

01:29:39.589 --> 01:29:40.619
Lunch?

01:29:41.389 --> 01:29:43.629
It was tough in this cold weather, right?

01:29:44.629 --> 01:29:47.859
Didn't you say you two visited the beach?

01:29:48.199 --> 01:29:49.229
No.

01:29:49.469 --> 01:29:50.968
We had lunch and went to a doll workshop.

01:29:50.969 --> 01:29:52.599
- You made those, right?
- Yes.

01:29:57.039 --> 01:30:00.238
- Hee Dong is being cold, isn't he?
- Yes.

01:30:00.239 --> 01:30:01.279
(Hee Dong seems cold.)

01:30:02.879 --> 01:30:05.648
You look greedy with food in both hands.

01:30:05.649 --> 01:30:07.418
I'm ambidextrous.

01:30:07.419 --> 01:30:08.419
Is that so?

01:30:08.420 --> 01:30:10.218
I'm still eating my meat.

01:30:10.219 --> 01:30:13.089
(The two seem quite close.)

01:30:15.489 --> 01:30:17.329
They were getting along just fine.

01:30:18.059 --> 01:30:20.058
Watching them make fun of each other...

01:30:20.059 --> 01:30:23.168
made me realize the two had become close.

01:30:23.169 --> 01:30:24.469
- Of course.
- Right.

01:30:25.299 --> 01:30:28.869
To be frank, Hee Dong and I have barely had a conversation.

01:30:29.439 --> 01:30:31.138
The two spent the whole day together,

01:30:31.139 --> 01:30:33.579
so I'm sure they talked a lot.

01:30:33.939 --> 01:30:37.548
Yes, it was a bummer.

01:30:37.549 --> 01:30:38.549
(She and Hee Dong have become distant in a day.)

01:30:39.979 --> 01:30:44.249
I'm most interested in Hee Dong.

01:30:45.489 --> 01:30:47.659
My heart fluttered more than anything else.

01:30:48.589 --> 01:30:51.058
Now that's a real love triangle.

01:30:51.059 --> 01:30:53.659
What's going on with the three kids?

01:30:59.439 --> 01:31:01.869
(After today's date, )

01:31:02.369 --> 01:31:07.009
(where will the three's story head next?)

01:31:12.479 --> 01:31:17.519
(Epilogue: Before Heading Out on Today's Morning Date)

01:31:19.219 --> 01:31:22.058
(Hee Dong is all alone...)

01:31:22.059 --> 01:31:26.699
(after everyone has gone out for their dates.)

01:32:05.499 --> 01:32:09.339
(Hee Dong has stopped by the Letter Room.)

01:32:11.909 --> 01:32:18.979
(Before leaving for her date, Si Woo left a letter for Hee Dong.)

01:32:28.219 --> 01:32:32.459
(Checking his mailbox)

01:32:33.099 --> 01:32:35.829
(A note can be seen through the gap.)

01:32:49.649 --> 01:32:54.619
(He can't open the mailbox.)

01:33:02.019 --> 01:33:04.629
(Maybe with these?)

01:33:14.969 --> 01:33:18.509
(You Hee Dong)

01:33:23.049 --> 01:33:26.248
(In the end, Hee Dong leaves for his date...)

01:33:26.249 --> 01:33:29.449
(without being able to read the letter.)

01:33:29.849 --> 01:33:32.148
(You Hee Dong)

01:33:32.149 --> 01:33:39.999
(Si Woo's feelings could not reach Hee Dong.)

01:33:40.873 --> 01:33:42.613
(1-on-1 Rotation Chat)

01:33:43.043 --> 01:33:45.883
(I chose you for both selections.)

01:33:46.353 --> 01:33:49.013
(Joke around with me too.)

01:33:50.123 --> 01:33:53.253
(I chose you for the Attraction Selection.)

01:33:53.353 --> 01:33:54.523
I'm like that too.

01:33:54.593 --> 01:33:57.993
(Time when they shared their true feelings)

01:33:58.193 --> 01:34:00.263
(A roller coaster of emotions)

01:34:00.533 --> 01:34:02.332
(1st-come 1st-served Date asked by the daughters)

01:34:02.333 --> 01:34:04.032
(Do we ask now?)

01:34:04.033 --> 01:34:05.703
Hold on.

01:34:05.933 --> 01:34:08.003
(Who did the daughters choose that shocked everyone?)

01:34:08.073 --> 01:34:10.203
Hold on a minute. What just happened?

01:34:10.627 --> 01:34:12.627
Dramaday.me